                    </p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="relative z-10 shrink-0">
                    <span class="bg-white text-red-base font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-xs px-8 py-4 rounded-full group-hover:bg-navy-dark group-hover:text-white transition-colors inline-block shadow-md">
